Execution plan, changed-files, risk-assessment, review-packet, final-summary, and red/green + full gate logs written to `.ralph/runs/2026-07-05_204654_normal_run/`. State, progress, HANDOFF, and slice status updated. Sharpened the next slice **003H** with the verified demo-account→role-context map and the caveat that no demo account reaches the `management` context (use a mocked fixture there).

I did **not** commit — per the workflow the orchestrator independently validates and commits passing work. Next queued slice: **003H-dashboard-task-ui-wiring** (its 003G2 dependency is now satisfied).
